high_descs: Turn right and walk straight to the dining room to reach the diningtable.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Walk to the microwave on the left.
Slice the potato in the microwave.
Put the knife on the shelf.
Take out a slice of potato from the microwave.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Cool the slice of potato in the fridge and take it out.
Turn left to reach the diningtable.
Put the potato on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled potato on the diningtable.

high_descs: Walk around the diningtable ahead and then keep going straight towards the two doorways, entering the one on the left.
Pick up the knife from the table in front of you.
Walk around the table to get to the microwave on the left.
Open the microwave and slice the potato inside.
Place the knife down on the shelf.
Pick up one slice of potato.
Turn around to the fridge ahead.
Place the potato slice in the fridge, let it cool, then remove it.
Walk back to the diningtable where you picked the knife up from.
Place the slice of potato down on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Slice a potato, cool one slice inside a fridge, and place that potato slice on a diningtable.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the diningtable.
Take the knife from the table.
Turn around and go near the microwave oven.
There is a potato in the microwave oven.
Cut the potato into pieces using the knife on the shelf.
Then put the potato on the wardrobe.
Tale the piece of potato from the oven.
Put the potato into the refrigerator and cooled it.
Then take it out and go near the diningtable.
Put the potato piece on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Placed the potato on the diningtable.
